author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Planar Semiconductor plans to delist from Hamburg Stock Exchange
text:
Oct 21 Planar Semiconductor AG :
* Plans to delist from unofficial market and HIGH RISK MARKET segment of Stock Exchange in Hamburg
* Expects to delist by end of 2015
